&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About the role&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal Account Executive will have a strong understanding of the programmatic advertising ecosystem, audience targeting, and digital media activation. This individual will play a critical role in driving revenue growth by developing relationships with agencies, trading desks, and brands while educating clients on the value of InMarket&#39;s audience, identity, and measurement solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is an enthusiastic and outgoing self-starter who thrives in a fast-paced environment and enjoys building new business opportunities. They possess strong communication and relationship-building skills, a consultative sales approach, and a passion for helping clients solve complex marketing challenges through data-driven solutions.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role will partner closely with Sales Directors and cross-functional teams to identify, develop, and close new business opportunities across the programmatic ecosystem.&lt;/p&gt;
