&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Prospect, prioritize, and qualify new business opportunities across agencies, trading desks, DSPs, and direct brands.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Generate a high volume of sales activities, including outreach, meetings, presentations, proposals, and follow-up communications.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Partner with Sales Directors to drive revenue growth and expand InMarket&#39;s presence within the programmatic advertising ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the sales process by preparing proposals, audience recommendations, case studies, and strategic sales materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage RFPs, audience recommendations, and client requests for prospects and existing customers.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Develop a strong understanding of InMarket&#39;s audience, identity, activation, and measurement solutions and effectively communicate their value to clients.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build relationships with key stakeholders across agencies, brands, DSPs, and data partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take a data-driven approach to territory planning, pipeline management, and opportunity prioritization.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Product, Client Success, Sales Operations, and Marketing to deliver an exceptional customer experience.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Stay current on industry trends, programmatic technologies, privacy developments, and changes across the advertising ecosystem.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
