&lt;p&gt;At InMarket, AI is the default way of working, and we care less about where you come from than about what you&#39;ve built with it. Strong candidates come from a software engineering background or from a business domain (finance, marketing, operations), where they&#39;ve rebuilt a real workflow around AI.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This role is a great fit if you&#39;re looking at AI transformation and figuring out how it actually drives business value, playing with the latest tools, building things for fun, and are hungry to show what you can do at the highest levels of a fast-growing company.&lt;/p&gt;
