&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the end-to-end lifecycle of internal tools, from initial discovery, design, and rapid prototyping through launch, iteration, and transition to steady-state ownership.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Design and build scalable, AI-enabled systems and services that automate repetitive tasks and optimize complex workflows.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Modernize technical debt by converting ad-hoc scripts and notebook-driven processes into robust, maintainable, well-documented production software.&lt;/li&gt;
